---

<Layout
  title="Ventures — Mediainc"
  description="25 years of founding, developing and exiting companies across media, content and culture-adjacent industries — Cimientos, Folio, La Tempestad, Vocero, Trama and more."
>
  <Carousel
    images={mainBannerImages}
    alt="Empresas Mediáticas"
    height="h-[310px]"
    fit="cover"
    interval={4500}
  />

  <section class="py-8 flex flex-col gap-6 font-medium font-['EB_Garamond'] text-center">
    <h1 class="sr-only">Ventures</h1>
    <p class="text-[30px] leading-[1.2] font-medium">
      Over the past 25 years, Media Inc has participated in founding,
      developing, and exiting companies across media, content, and
      culture-adjacent industries.

      These are not archived history. They represent a continuous process of
      building: understanding what creates value in a specific context, and
      knowing when to transform, sell, or close.

      This track record informs everything Media Inc builds today.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="w-full md:w-4/5">
      <Carousel
        images={cimientosImages}
        alt="Cimientos"
        height="h-[450px]"
        fit="auto"
        interval={4500}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center self-stretch">
      <img src="/uploads/2019/06/03.png" alt="Cimientos logo" class="w-50 h-auto object-contain"/>
      <time
        datetime="2018"
        class="mt-1 text-[16px] leading-[1] text-[#B5B5B5] uppercase tracking-wide"
        >2018 - 2020</time
      >
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#D4D4D4] leading-[1.5] tracking-wide text-[14px]">
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="w-full md:w-4/5">
      <Carousel
        images={folioImages}
        alt="Folio"
        height="h-[450px]"
        fit="auto"
        interval={4500}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center self-stretch">
      <img src="/uploads/Folio-Blanco.png" alt="Cimientos logo" class="w-40 h-auto object-contain"/>
      <time
        datetime="2009"
        class="mt-1 text-[16px] leading-[1] text-[#B5B5B5] uppercase tracking-wide"
        >2009 - 2017</time
      >
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#D4D4D4] leading-[1.5] tracking-wide text-[14px]">
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="w-full md:w-4/5">
      <Carousel
        images={tempestadImages}
        alt="La Tempestad"
        height="h-[450px]"
        fit="auto"
        interval={4500}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center self-stretch">
      <img src="/uploads/2019/06/LT_logow.png" alt="La Tempestad logo" class="w-full h-auto object-contain"/>
      <time
        datetime="1998"
        class="mt-1 text-[16px] leading-[1] text-[#B5B5B5] uppercase tracking-wide"
        >1998 - 2017</time
      >
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#D4D4D4] leading-[1.5] tracking-wide text-[14px]">
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="w-full md:w-4/5">
      <Carousel
        images={voceroImages}
        alt="Vocero"
        height="h-[450px]"
        fit="auto"
        interval={4500}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center self-stretch">
      <img src="/uploads/2019/06/vocero_logob.png" alt="Vocero logo" class="w-full h-auto object-contain"/>
      <time
        datetime="2005"
        class="mt-1 text-[16px] leading-[1] text-[#B5B5B5] uppercase tracking-wide"
        >2005 - 2017</time
      >
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#D4D4D4] leading-[1.5] tracking-wide text-[14px]">
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="w-full md:w-4/5">
      <Carousel
        images={tramaImages}
        alt="Trama"
        height="h-[450px]"
        fit="auto"
        interval={4500}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center self-stretch">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">
        Trama
      </h2>
      <time
        datetime="2012"
        class="mt-1 text-[16px] leading-[1] text-[#B5B5B5] uppercase tracking-wide"
        >2012 - 2015</time
      >
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#D4D4D4] leading-[1.5] tracking-wide text-[14px]">
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
